short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically opens Google Meet links for your scheduled meetings.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Never miss a meeting again. Set a timer, and automatically get put in the Google Meet waiting room in a new tab for all the Meetings you have accepted invitations to! Decide yourself if you want to enter 5 minutes early, or use it as a reminder to open meetings 2 min after as a backup reminder.
